HOST YOUR EVENT
HOST YOUR EVENT
The best parties are beach parties.
Ask us about hosting your next gathering with us at Santiago’s Florida Kitchen & Craft Bar, located inside our location at Guy Harvey Resort St. Augustine Beach. With outdoor and indoor event space available, you can host your event in our restaurant, or talk to us about hosting your event in the spacious ballroom or conference room at the resort!
4,000 sq. feet of event space, including restaurant/bar, conference room and ballroom for larger events
Beautiful outdoor patio terrace located adjacent to ballroom, perfect for mixers/receptions
Outdoor dining space adjacent to restaurant
Audio/visual rental including projector screen
Table and chair linens rental
Fully customizable menus
Bar tender service
Hosted, open or cash bars
